Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/jnrwebdev/dotfiles.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Add submodules/plugins

	git submodule add http://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive.git bundle/fugitive
	git add .
	git commit -m "Install Fugitive.vim bundle as a submodule."

Install to another machine

	cd ~
	git clone http://github.com/jnrwebdev/dotfiles.git ~/.vim
	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
        ln -s ~/.vim/config ~/.config/terminator/config
	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule init
	git submodule update
